OL,3,CParliament to debate planning laws
OL,4,Cafter construction of giant warehouse
OL,6,FA debate on historic planning consents
OL,7,Fwill be held in parliament today,
OL,8,Fafter work started to build a stadium-
OL,9,Fsize warehouse near homes in a rural
OL,10,FSouth Gloucestershire village.
OL,12,FLocal MP Claire Young is expected to
OL,13,Fcall on the government to introduce
OL,14,Fnew legislation to allow modern
OL,15,Fconditions to be placed on these
OL,16,Fdevelopments.
OL,18,FThe warehouse, which is described as
OL,19,Fan industrial distribution hub, will
OL,20,Fbe more than 20 metres tall and
OL,21,F500,000 sq ft once it is completed.
