OL,3,CParliament to debate planning laws
OL,4,Cafter construction of giant warehouse
OL,6,FNearby residents in Pilning say the
OL,7,Fstructure has already devalued their
OL,8,Fhomes and drastically changed their
OL,9,Fcommunity.
OL,11,FOne resident told ITV News West
OL,12,FCountry, "How have they been allowed
OL,13,Fto build it so close to our
OL,14,Fproperties? It's made everything dark,
OL,15,Fthe constant noise and dust."
OL,17,FResident Nick Gannon added: "It's just
OL,18,Fso big and so impactful and affecting
OL,19,Fpeople's lives. The issue is, it seems
OL,20,Fthere's nothing we can do about it."
