OL,3,CParliament to debate planning laws
OL,4,Cafter construction of giant warehouse
OL,6,FSouth Gloucestershire Council says it
OL,7,Fwas unable to stop the build of the
OL,8,Fcontroversial warehouse due to
OL,9,Fhistoric planning permission granted
OL,10,Ffor the Severnside area in 1957.
OL,12,FCabinet member for planning, Cllr
OL,13,FChris Willmore, explained: "This all
OL,14,Fgoes back to a planning consent that
OL,15,Fwas granted in 1957, nearly 70 years
OL,16,Fago, before most people were born and
OL,17,Fwe're stuck with it.
OL,26,@uD@\OU
