OL,3,CParliament to debate planning laws
OL,4,Cafter construction of giant warehouse
OL,6,F"It was granted before modern rules
OL,7,Fabout the amenity of residents, before
OL,8,Fall the wildlife and ecological
OL,9,Fprotections we would normally put on a
OL,10,Fplanning consent. The council can do
OL,11,Fsome small things but basically its
OL,12,Fstuck with a consent that was already
OL,13,Fgranted."
OL,15,FMs Willmore has worked closely with
OL,16,FClaire Young MP to call on the
OL,17,Fgovernment to intervene. But she added
OL,18,Fthat the decision to approve the
OL,19,Fwarehouse in the first place was
OL,20,F"heartbreaking".
