OL,3,CParliament to debate planning laws
OL,4,Cafter construction of giant warehouse
OL,6,F"There's absolutely nothing we could
OL,7,Fdo. We've tried in the past. We've
OL,8,Fsought legal opinion from leading
OL,9,Flawyers, we've challenged the 1957
OL,10,Fconsent in the courts and on planning
OL,11,Fappeals.
OL,13,F"But we've been overruled by the
OL,14,Fcourts and the Secretary of State.
OL,15,FPeople are sitting on those planning
OL,16,Fcommittees having to take decisions
OL,17,Fthey don't want to take. It's
OL,18,Fheartbreaking for the residents and
OL,19,Fits heartbreaking for the councillors.
OL,26,@nD@AOU
