OL,3,CParliament to debate planning laws
OL,4,Cafter construction of giant warehouse
OL,6,F"This is a national issue. There was a
OL,7,Fsimilar issue with the quarrying
OL,8,Fconsent. The government put
OL,9,Flegislation that enabled councils to
OL,10,Fput modern conditions on those
OL,11,Fconsents.
OL,13,F"They've not yet bitten the bullet on
OL,14,Fthese other consents. The solution
OL,15,Flies in Westminster with the
OL,16,Fgovernment introducing legislation to
OL,17,Flet the council sort out these old
OL,18,Fconsents."
OL,26,@nD@AOUzD@JO]
