OL,3,CParliament to debate planning laws
OL,4,Cafter construction of giant warehouse
OL,6,FA government minister will respond to
OL,7,Fthe debate on Thursday 11 December,
OL,8,Fbut they have issued a statement.
OL,10,FA spokesperson for the Ministry of
OL,11,FHousing, Communities and Local
OL,12,FGovernment said: "We're taking
OL,13,Fdecisive action to update the planning
OL,14,Fsystem and get Britain building, while
OL,15,Fensuring communities are engaged with
OL,16,Fdevelopers' plans.
OL,18,F"Councils are ultimately responsible
OL,19,Ffor reviewing old permissions if the
OL,20,Fdevelopment is no longer suitable and
OL,21,Fdeciding whether action is necessary."
